[[File:Surface_analysis.gif|thumb]]正在发展，之后成为飓风]]
'''地面天气图'''是特殊类型的[[天气图|天气图]]，根据地面气象站提供的信息在指定区域地图上标出特定时间[[天气|天气]]元素<ref>{{cite book | title = Air Apparent: How Meteorologists Learned to Map, Predict, and Dramatize Weather | publisher = University of Chicago Press | year = 1999 | isbn = 9780226534237 | author = Mark Monmonier | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | url = https://press.uchicago.edu/ucp/books/book/chicago/A/bo3629614.html | archive-date = 2020-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200110130325/https://www.press.uchicago.edu/ucp/books/book/chicago/A/bo3629614.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。天气图需要标明并追踪的数据包括[[气压|海平面气压]]、[[温度|温度]]和[[云量|云量]]，将这些信息标上地图有助于气象学家寻找[[锋_(气象)|锋]]等[[天气尺度|天气尺度]]特征。

19世纪诞生的首批天气图都是在事后绘制，用于帮助设立风暴天气系统理论<ref name="MILLER">{{cite journal | author = Eric R. Miller | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/061/mwr-061-07-0189.pdf | title = American Pioneers in Meteorology | journal = Monthly Weather Review | volume = 61 | number = 7 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170225115821/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/061/mwr-061-07-0189.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2017-02-25 | accessdate = 2017-02-25 | date = 1933-07 | editor = W. J. Humphreys | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。[[电报|电报]]问世让同步[[地表天气观测|地表天气观测]]首度成为可能，[[史密森尼学会|史密森尼学会]]在19世纪40年代后期成为人类历史上第一个绘制实时天气分析图的机构。美国率先采用地面天气图，后于19世纪70年代传到世界各地。20世纪10年代后期，欧洲普通开始利用[[挪威气象模型|挪威气象模型]]分析锋，并在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间传到美国。

地面天气图使用特殊符号代表锋、云量、[[降水|降水]]及其他重要信息。例如用字母“{{lang|en|H}}”代表[[高气压|高气压]]，说明当地天气晴朗，气温偏高。字母“{{lang|en|L}}”常用于代表[[低气压|低气压]]，往往伴随降水。各种符号不仅用于标识锋区及其他地面天气边界，还能标明天气图各个地点的当前天气。降水范围有助于确定锋的类型和位置。

== 地面天气图历史 ==
[[Image:10_PM_March_12_surface_analysis_of_Great_Blizzard_of_1888.png|thumb]]的地面天气图]]

人类从19世纪开始利用天气图设立风暴天气系统理论，这也是人类首次从现代角度利用天气图<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.intelltheory.com/galton.shtml | title = Francis Galton | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200507224358/https://www.intelltheory.com/galton.shtml | publisher = Human Intelligence | archivedate = 2020-05-07 }}</ref>。1845年[[电报|电报]]网的发展让快速收集多地天气信息用于实时分析成为可能，[[史密森尼学会|史密森尼学会]]从19世纪40年代到60年代在美国东部和中期大部分地区建立观测网<ref>{{cite web | author = Frank Rives Millikan | publisher = Smithsonian Institution | archivedate = 2006-12-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.si.edu/archives/ihd/jhp/joseph03.htm | title = Joseph Henry: Father of the Weather Service | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061230073137/https://www.si.edu/archives/ihd/jhp/joseph03.htm | accessdate = 2006-12-30 }}</ref>。

各气象站的建造时间不同，所以早期收集的天气数据作用有限。英国是第一个尝试时间标准化的国家，1855年时已基本确立[[格林威治标准时间|格林威治标准时间]]，美国直到1905年[[底特律|底特律]]设立标准时间才开始受到时区影响。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.webexhibits.org/daylightsaving/d.html | title = Daylight Saving Time | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820190314/http://www.webexhibits.org/daylightsaving/d.html | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | work = webexhibits.org | publisher = IDEA | archivedate = 2020-08-20 }}</ref>1873年，其他国家开始跟随美国的脚步同步观测天气<ref>{{cite book | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170926041201/https://celebrating200years.noaa.gov/foundations/weather/#expand | archivedate = 2017-09-26 | url = https://celebrating200years.noaa.gov/foundations/weather/#expand | title = General Myer: Establishing a Legacy of Weather Service | chapter = An Expanding Presence | accessdate = 2020-08-30 }}</ref>，然后又开始为地面天气图准备。虽然1841年就有科学家提出类似构想，但直到20世纪10年代后期挪威气象模型问世后，人类才开始在天气图上标识锋区<ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Schultz | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181223211442/http://www.cimms.ou.edu/~schultz/sanders/sanders.pdf | archivedate = 2018-12-23 | url = http://www.cimms.ou.edu/~schultz/sanders/sanders.pdf | title = Perspectives on Fred Sanders's Research on Cold Fronts | date = 2003 | edition = 2004, 2006 | page = 5 | accessdate = 2018-12-23 | format = PDF }}</ref>。空气密度变化的边缘与[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]][[前线|前线]]（{{lang|en|Military front}}）位置接近，科学家便采用“锋”（{{lang|en|front}}）来代表天气图上的这类线条<ref>{{cite web | publisher = [[澳洲氣象局|Bureau of Meteorology]] | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/info/ftweather/page_6.shtml | title = Air Masses and Weather Maps | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191101060558/http://www.bom.gov.au/info/ftweather/page_6.shtml | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2019-11-01 | archivedate = 2019-11-01 }}</ref>。

[[Image:Weather_symbolsNEW2.png|thumb]]

第一次世界大战结束后，挪威气旋模型很快传入美国，但该国此后数十年都没有正式分析锋，直到1947年6月气象局－空军－海军分析中心（{{lang|en|Weather Bureau-Air Force-Navy Analysis Center}}）在[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]市中心成立才改变局面<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820201932/https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/html/WPC_history.pdf | deadurl = no | url = https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/html/WPC_history.pdf | title = Summary of WPC's Heritage and Leadership | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | archivedate = 2020-08-20 | format = PDF }}</ref>。1969年，美国开始尝试天气图绘制自动化<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.ncep.noaa.gov/officenotes/NOAA-NPM-NCEPON-0001/013FD50A.pdf | title = Prospectus for an NMC Digital Facsimile Incoder Mapping Program | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | date = 1969-01 | author1 = U. S. Department of Commerce | author2 = Environmental Science Services Administration | author3 = Weather Bureau | author4 = National Meteorological Center | archive-date = 2016-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223233808/http://www.ncep.noaa.gov/officenotes/NOAA-NPM-NCEPON-0001/013FD50A.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并在20世纪70年代达成目标。1987年，[[香港|香港]]也已实现地面天气图自动绘制<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.hko.gov.hk/sc/wservice/tsheet/computer.htm | title = 天文台的电脑系统及应用 | author = 香港天文台 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | archive-date = 2020-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200903071408/https://www.hko.gov.hk/sc/wservice/tsheet/computer.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1999年，计算机软硬件的进步已经具备充分的处理能力，可以在单台工作站叠加卫星图像、雷达图像，以及大气厚度和[[锋生|锋生]]等模型派生领域数据，结合地面观测绘制最理想的地面天气图。美国是在使用多台[[高级交互式气象处理系统|高级交互式气象处理系统]]（{{lang|en|Advanced Weather Interactive Processing System}}）工作站取代[[鹰图|鹰图]]（{{lang|en|Intergraph}}）工作站后实现上述目标。<ref>{{cite web | author = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | url = https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/html/Accomplish99/Accomplish99.html | title = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center 1999 Accomplishment Report | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | archivedate = 2018-02-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180206150606/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/html/Accomplish99/Accomplish99.html }}</ref>2001年，[[国家气象局_(美国)|美国国家气象局]]所绘各种地面天气图与另外四家机构的数据合并，成为每六小时发布一次的统一地面天气图（{{lang|en|Unified Surface Analysis}}）<ref name="DR">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807024811/https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/sfc/UASfcManualVersion1.pdf | url = https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/sfc/UASfcManualVersion1.pdf | title = Unified Surface Analysis Manual | date = 2013-11-21 | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | author1 = Weather Prediction Center | author2 = Ocean Prediction Center | author3 = National Hurricane Center | author4 = Honolulu Forecast Office | archivedate = 2020-08-07 | format = PDF }}</ref>。近年来，人类在[[气象学|气象学]]和[[地理信息系统|地理信息系统]]取得的进步令精细定制天气图成为可能，天气信息能够迅速匹配关联地理细节。例如结冰情况能够映射到公路网络，这种手段有望在可预见的将来改变地面天气图的创建和显示方式。<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Saseendran S. A. | author2 = Harenduprakash L. | author3 = Rathore L. S. | author4 = Singh S. V. | url = http://www.gisdevelopment.net/application/environment/conservation/envm0004.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924022312/http://www.gisdevelopment.net/application/environment/conservation/envm0004.htm | title = A GIS application for weather analysis and forecasting | archivedate = 2015-09-24 | location = New Delhi | publisher = Department of Science and Technology | work = National Centre for Medium Range Weather Forecasting | accessdate = 2015-09-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

== 气象站模型在天气图的应用 ==
[[Image:Station_model.gif|thumb]]

绘制天气图需在各气象站配备气象站模型，这些模型会将温度、[[露点|露点]]、[[风速|风速]]、[[风向|风向]]、气压、气压趋势以及当前天气绘制成图<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service | archivedate = 2009-09-16 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/ohx/educate/station_model.gif | title = Station Model Example | accessdate = 2009-09-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090916093550/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/ohx/educate/station_model.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>。中间的圆圈代表云量，里面填写的分数代表[[陰天|阴云]]程度<ref>{{cite web | author = Dr Elizabeth R. Tuttle | url = http://www.du.edu/~etuttle/weather/weather.htm | title = Weather Maps | archivedate = 2015-02-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150209150529/http://mysite.du.edu/~etuttle/weather/weather.htm | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2020-08-31 }}</ref>。美国以外地区采用[[摄氏温标|摄氏温标]]标示温度和露点。风旗指向风的方向，每一面满旗代表每小时18.52公里风速，半旗代表每小时9.26公里。风速达到每小时92.6公里后，每个实心三角形代表每小时92.6公里风速。<ref>{{cite web | author = American Meteorological Society | archivedate = 2020-04-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200403052349/https://www.ametsoc.org/amsedu/dstreme/extras/wxsym2.html | url = https://www.ametsoc.org/amsedu/dstreme/extras/wxsym2.html | title = Selected DataStreme Atmosphere Weather Map Symbols | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2004-10-21 }}</ref>。美国气象站模型绘制天气图时降雨量的单位是[[英寸|英寸]]，国际标准是[[毫米|毫米]]。气象站模型完成绘制后，天气图上会有[[等高線|等压线]]、等变压线、等温线和等风速线用于分析。<ref>{{cite web | author = CoCoRAHS | url = http://ccc.atmos.colostate.edu/~hail/teachers/lessons/isopleths.htm | title = INTRODUCTION TO DRAWING ISOPLETHS | accessdate = 2009-02-12 | archivedate = 2009-02-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090212165051/http://ccc.atmos.colostate.edu/~hail/teachers/lessons/isopleths.htm }}</ref>

== 天气尺度特征 ==
天气尺度特征通常规模偏大，长度在数百公里以上<ref>{{cite web | author = Glossary of meteorology | url = http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Synoptic_scale | title = Synoptic scale | publisher = American Meteorological Society | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200505073840/http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Synoptic_scale | archivedate = 2020-05-05 | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 气压中心 ===
[[File:Wind_barbs.gif|thumb]]
地面高气压和低气压的中心位于地面天气图闭合等压线内，一定是圈定区域内气压最高或最低的位置，能够一目了然地标明附近天气情况。英语國家的天气图一般用“{{lang|en|H}}”代表高气压，“{{lang|en|L}}”代表低气压<ref>{{cite web | author = Weather Doctor | url = http://www.islandnet.com/~see/weather/elements/high.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913140040/http://www.islandnet.com/~see/weather/elements/high.htm | deadurl = yes | title = Weather's Highs and Lows: Part 1 The High | archivedate = 2019-09-13 | accessdate = 2020-08-31 }}</ref>，西班牙语国家則大多用“{{lang|en|A}}”代表高气压，“{{lang|en|B}}”代表低气压<ref>{{cite web | author = Agencia Estatal de Meteorología | publisher = AEMET | title = Meteorología del aeropuerto de La Palma | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120219163805/http://www.aemet.es/en/divulgacion/aeronautica/detalles/Meteorologia_del_aeropuerto_de_La_Palma | archivedate = 2012-02-19 | accessdate = 2012-02-19 | url = http://www.aemet.es/en/divulgacion/aeronautica/detalles/Meteorologia_del_aeropuerto_de_La_Palma }}</ref>。

==== 低气压 ====
低气压天气系统又称[[气旋|气旋]]，通常在天气图气压区内气压最低的位置。受[[科里奥利力|科里奥利力]]影响，北半球地表的气旋以逆时针方向旋转，南半球朝顺时针方向旋转。气旋附近的天气通常很不稳定，云量增多、风速加快、温度升高，大气向上运动，导致降水几率提升。冷空气掠过冰面时，有可能在温度不高的洋面形成[[極地低壓|極地低壓]]。相对温暖的海水促使气流上升，形成低气压，此时的降水通常是降雪。热带气旋和冬季风暴就是强烈的低气压，陆地上的[[热低压|热低压]]通常代表夏季炎热天气。<ref>{{cite web | work = BBC Weather | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110113054028/https://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/features/basics_lowpressure.shtml | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/features/basics_lowpressure.shtml | title = Weather Basics - Low Pressure | accessdate = 2011-01-13 | archivedate = 2011-01-13 | date = 2004-05 }}</ref>

==== 高气压 ====
高气压天气系统又称[[反气旋|反气旋]]，在北半球地面以顺时针方向旋转，南半球向逆时针方向旋转。地面高气压下方的大气会下沉，进而因空气压缩导致气温略有上升，天空万里无云，风速缓慢，降水几率很小。<ref>{{cite web | work = BBC Weather | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/features/understanding/highpressure.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110205130252/http://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/features/understanding/highpressure.shtml | title = High Pressure | archivedate = 2011-02-05 | accessdate = 2011-02-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>下沉的空气很干燥，所以升温需要的能量少，如果高气压持续，大气沉降会令污染物在地表附近聚集，进而导致空气污染<ref>{{cite web | work = United Kingdom School System | archivedate = 2009-09-16 | accessdate = 2009-09-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090916093041/http://atschool.eduweb.co.uk/radgeog/metlink/ppt/highs/Press-System.ppt | url = http://atschool.eduweb.co.uk/radgeog/metlink/ppt/highs/Press-System.ppt | title = Pressure, Wind and Weather Systems | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

=== 锋 ===<!-- This section is linked from [[高速氣流|Jet stream]] -->
{{Main|锋 (气象)}}
[[Image:Occluded_cyclone.svg|thumb]]的交汇处]]

气象学上所说的锋是指移动[[气团|气团]]前缘，其密度、气温和[[湿度|湿度]]均与前方入侵的气团不同。气团经过期间，当地气温、温度、风速、风向、气压都会改变，降水格局通常也会变化。无论是变暖还是变冷，这种变化都称为锋。冷空气通常从极地高压区朝赤道移动，与低气压天气系统的暖湿气流相互影响就会形成[[冷锋|冷锋]]。冷锋位于移动的冷空气团前沿，如果是在北半球，通常还会以逆时针方向把低气压区基本包裹起来。赤道沿线边缘的高空极地高速气流附近可能形成极地锋。锋由高空风引导，但移动速度通常不及风速。北半球的锋大多从西向东移动，也能从北向南，并包裹气团关联的低气压区。锋的移动大多源自[[壓強梯度力|壓強梯度力]]和地球自转产生的科里奥利力，山区和大范围水域都能扰乱锋区。<ref name="DR"/>

==== 冷锋 ====
{{Main|冷锋}}
冷锋位于地面天气图温度下降范围的前沿，分析等温线时显示为等温线梯度前沿，通常在尖锐的地面[[低壓槽|低壓槽]]内。冷锋的移动速度可以达到暖锋两倍并导致天气剧烈变化，冷空气密度大于暖空气，所以入侵时能迅速抬升暖空气。冷锋通常还会伴随[[雨带|雨带]]和[[雷暴|雷暴]]出现。天气图用蓝色箭头代表冷锋，箭头指向冷空气前进方向前沿。<ref name="DR"/>

==== 暖锋 ====
{{Main|暖锋}}
[[Image:Warmfrontai.svg|thumb]]]]

位于地面的暖空气团驱逐冷空气时，暖空气团的前沿就叫[[暖锋|暖锋]]。等温线梯度朝赤道方向的边缘温度上升，暖锋通常也在低压槽内，但比冷锋存在的低压槽要宽。暖空气密度不及，所以难以取代地表的冷空气，移动速度不及冷锋，进而导致暖锋内的气温差异更大。暖空气在高海拔地区更容易取代冷空气并引起温度变化，暖锋前面的云大部分是[[层云|层云]]，降水随暖锋逼近增多。暖锋经过前经常形成[[霧|霧]]，经过后天气往往很快放晴，气温上升。如果暖空气不稳定，混合暖湿气流后会在暖锋前方的层云内形成雷暴。暖锋过去后，雷雨可能继续。天气图上通常用半圆形红色线条代表暖锋及其移动方向。<ref name="DR"/>

==== 锢囚锋 ====
{{Main|锢囚锋}}
[[Image:NWS_weather_fronts.svg|thumb]]的各种符号：<br />
1. 冷锋<br />
2. 暖锋<br />
3. 准静止锋<br />
4. 锢囚锋<br />
5. 地面低压槽<br />
6. 飑线<br />
7. 干线<br />
8. 东风波<br />
9. 暖舌]]

[[锢囚锋|锢囚锋]]是在冷锋替换暖锋引起[[气旋生成|气旋生成]]的过程中形成<ref>{{cite web | publisher = University of Illinois | url = http://ww2010.atmos.uiuc.edu/(Gl)/guides/mtr/af/frnts/ofdef.rxml | title = Occluded Front | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200725195532/http://ww2010.atmos.uiuc.edu/%28Gl%29/guides/mtr/af/frnts/ofdef.rxml | archivedate = 2020-07-25 | accessdate = 2020-08-31 }}</ref>。冷锋和暖锋自然地向两极方向弯曲进入锢囚点，在气象学上又称三相点<ref>{{cite web | publisher = National Weather Service Office, Norman, Oklahoma | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090130010024/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/oun/severewx/glossary4.php#t | author = Michael Branick | title = A Comprehensive Glossary of Weather Terms for Storm Spotters | accessdate = 2009-01-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/oun/severewx/glossary4.php#t | archivedate = 2009-01-30 }}</ref>。锢囚锋位于尖锐的低压槽内，但边缘后方的空团既可能是暖空气，也可能是冷空气。如果是冷锢囚锋，取代暖锋位置的气团温度低于暖锋前方冷空气，并在两个气团下方高速移动。如果是暖锢囚锋，取代暖锋位置的气团温度高于暖锋前方冷空气，位于冷空气团上方并抬升暖空气团。锢囚锋附近可能出现包括雷暴在内的各种天气，但大部分锢囚锋伴随的气团都很干燥。天气图上通常用紫色线条代表锢囚锋，并以半圆和三角形交替指明移动方向。<ref name="DR" />

暖舌指高空暖空气在地球表面的投影，可能在低气压的锢囚锋阶段形成<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eumetcal.org/resources/ukmeteocal/rapid_cyclo/www/english/glossary/trowalca.htm | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161014180920/http://www.eumetcal.org/resources/ukmeteocal/rapid_cyclo/www/english/glossary/trowalca.htm | deadurl = yes | archive-date = 2016-10-14 | title = Trowal | work = [[世界气象组织|World Meteorological Organisation]] | publisher = Eumetcal | access-date = 2016-10-14 }}</ref>。

==== 准静止锋和切变线 ====
{{Main|准静止锋|切变线}}
[[准静止锋|准静止锋]]指两气团间基本不移动的边界，两个气团都没有足够的能量挤开对方，所以长时间保留在原地，但还是会一波波地移动<ref>{{cite web | publisher = University of Illinois | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123528/http://ww2010.atmos.uiuc.edu/(Gl)/guides/mtr/af/frnts/sfdef.rxml | url = http://ww2010.atmos.uiuc.edu/(Gl)/guides/mtr/af/frnts/sfdef.rxml | title = Stationary Front | archivedate = 2020-08-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。准静止锋缩小到一定程度，风向能在短距离内变化时改称[[切变线|切变线]]<ref>{{cite web | work = Glossary of Meteorology | url = http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Shear_line | title = Shear Line | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200218144828/http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Shear_line | archivedate = 2020-02-18 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | publisher = American Meteorological Society }}</ref>。切变线碰到雷暴后可能推动[[熱帶氣旋|熱帶氣旋]]形成，也可能再度形成准静止锋。地面天气图以红点和虚线代表切变线。<ref name="DR"/>

== 中尺度特征 ==
中尺度特征比包括锋在内的天气尺度天气系统小，但比雷暴之类风暴尺度天气系统大，水平跨度通常在十到数百公里范围<ref>{{cite book | last = Fujita | first = T. T. | year = 1986 | chapter = Mesoscale classifications: their history and their application to forecasting | title = Mesoscale Meteorology and Forecasting | publisher = American Meteorological Society | location = Boston | pages = 18–35}}</ref>。

=== 乾線 ===
{{main|乾線}}
[[乾線|乾線]]是[[洛磯山脈|洛磯山脈]]和其他相同走向山脉东侧干、湿气团的边界，在地面天气图上通常位于露点、湿气和梯度前沿。靠近地表的暖湿空气密度大于温度更高、更干燥的空气，就像冷锋从暖空气下方楔入一样楔入干暖空气。<ref>{{cite web | author = Huaqing Cai | url = http://www.atmos.ucla.edu/~caihq/pic/fig23.html | title = Dryline cross section | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203103724/http://www.atmos.ucla.edu/~caihq/pic/fig23.html | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | accessdate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>干暖空气下方的暖湿空气温度升高后密度降低并向上移动，有时会形成雷暴<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.accd.edu/sac/earthsci/sgirhard/1370.090/chap3.htm | title = Lecture 3 | archivedate = 2008-09-20 | accessdate = 2008-09-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080920100551/http://www.accd.edu/sac/earthsci/sgirhard/1370.090/chap3.htm }}</ref>。

高空的干燥空气日间下降到地面，促使乾線明显向东移动。夜间没有太阳加热空气，下层大气混合，乾線回转向西<ref>{{cite journal | author = Lewis D. Grasso | date = 2008-08 | volume = 128 | issue = 8 | publisher = American Meteorological Society | journal = Monthly Weather Review | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | url = https://journals.ametsoc.org/mwr/article/128/8/2816/104696/A-Numerical-Simulation-of-Dryline-Sensitivity-to | title = A Numerical Simulation of Dryline Sensitivity to Soil Moisture | archive-date = 2020-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200903071434/https://journals.ametsoc.org/mwr/article/128/8/2816/104696/A-Numerical-Simulation-of-Dryline-Sensitivity-to | dead-url = no }}</ref>。如有足够水分汇聚，乾線可能成为下午和夜间雷暴活动的核心<ref>{{cite web | work = Glossary of Meteorology | archivedate = 2020-02-17 | deadurl = no | title = lee trough | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200217120236/http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Lee_trough | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | url = http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Lee_trough }}</ref>。地面天气图用棕色线条代表乾線，并以贝形弧形标明湿气方向，但这并不代表乾線的移动方向，这种情况在天气图上很少见<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190726225710/http://ww2010.atmos.uiuc.edu/(Gl)/guides/mtr/af/frnts/dfdef.rxml | publisher = University of Illinois | url = http://ww2010.atmos.uiuc.edu/(Gl)/guides/mtr/af/frnts/dfdef.rxml | title = Dry Line: A Moisture Boundary | accessdate = 2020-08-31 | archivedate = 2019-07-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 外流边界和飑线 ===
[[File:DangerousShelfCloud.jpg|thumb]]可能代表[[飑|飑]]随时出现]]

有组织的雷暴活动区不但能强化已经存在的锋区，还能取代冷锋。这种情况通常在高空高速气流分裂成两部分时出现。高空气流分裂，在下层[[内流_(气象学)|内流]]最有利的位置形成[[中尺度对流系统|中尺度对流系统]]。对流朝东面和赤道方向移动，进入气温更高的地区。对流足够强劲并呈线形或弧形时，中尺度对流系统称为飑线，在地面天气图上标出前进方向的边缘，代表风向转变和气压上升的位置。<ref>{{cite web | work = Office of the Federal Coordinator for Meteorology | url = http://www.ofcm.gov/slso/pdf/slsochp2.pdf | title = Chapter 2: Definitions | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801141934/https://www.ofcm.gov/slso/pdf/slsochp2.pdf | archivedate = 2016-08-01 | accessdate = 2016-08-01 | format = PDF }}</ref>

=== 海陆风锋 ===
[[Image:LAKE_BREEZE-en.gif|thumb]]的理想循环模式]]

陆地在晴天加热上空大气，气温高于水温时便形成[[海陆风|海陆风]]锋。日间湖泊与河流的顺风口，以及夜间的海上陆地（如岛屿）也会形成类似锋。水的[[比熱容|比热]]很大，所以即使万里无云，水体的昼夜温差也不大。水温变化幅度通常不到一摄氏度，陆地因比热小，往往在数小时内就能升温或降温十余度。<ref name="seabreeze">{{cite web | work = Glossary of Meteorology | url = http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Sea_breeze | title = Sea Breeze | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200729231411/http://glossary.ametsoc.org/wiki/Sea_breeze | archivedate = 2020-07-29 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-08-31 }}</ref>

